<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc08dea77-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s19404"><num value="19404">§ 19404.</num><heading> Applicability</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This chapter shall apply with respect to a claim that is filed under Federal, State, or Tribal law on or after <date date="2022-12-07">December 7, 2022</date>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc08dea78-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/117/224/s5">Pub. L. 117–224, § 5</ref>, <date date="2022-12-07">Dec. 7, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/2292">136 Stat. 2292</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
